      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v8) is maintained under a documented SQA plan including Git-based version control, automated regression test suite (482 test cases), and formal issue tracking. All simulation scripts used in this COU are archived with SHA-256 checksums. SQA level meets the MRL 5 requirement."
    },
