      "rationale": "FDA pump experimental data were collected under controlled conditions: hematocrit 33±1%, temperature 37±0.5°C, phosphate-buffered saline with bovine blood. Instrumentation calibration certificates are on file. Test conditions are adequately documented for the MRL 5 assessment."
    },
    {
